thread.title: Ericsson signs multi-year broadcast services deal with Channel 5
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Ericsson signs multi-year broadcast services deal with Channel 5 | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Ericsson signs multi-year broadcast services deal with Channel 5
text:
Sept 10 Telefonaktiebolaget L M Ericsson
* Ericsson signs multi-year broadcast services deal with Channel 5
* Exclusive deal includes playout, media management, metadata, business continuity and access services
* Deal spans Channel 5's portfolio of terrestrial and digital channels in the UK Source text for Eikon: (Stockholm Newsroom)
